1. GET /todos (Get all todos)

curl -X GET http://localhost:8000/todos

2. GET /todos/{id} (Get todo by ID)
Replace {id} with the ID of the todo you want to retrieve.

curl -X GET http://localhost:8000/todos/{id}

3. POST /todos (Create new todo)

curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/todos -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"title": "New Task", "content": "Do something new"}'


4. PUT /todos/{id} (Update todo by ID)
Replace {id} with the ID of the todo you want to update.

curl -X PUT http://localhost:8000/todos/{id} -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"title": "Updated Task", "content": "Updated content"}'

5. DELETE /todos/{id} (Delete todo by ID)
Replace {id} with the ID of the todo you want to delete.

curl -X DELETE http://localhost:8000/todos/{id}